eing floated by many as a viable VP choice for Joe Biden. She even had a New York Times article on the subject. Here&#8217;s why that won&#8217;t work.</p></div><div class="author-meta post-meta"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/erick-erickson/" class="avatar"><img src="https://theresurgent.com/wp-content/uploads/erick-20-100x100.jpg" alt="Erick Erickson" class="avatar"></a> <span>by <a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/erick-erickson/">Erick Erickson</a></span></div><div class="post-meta time-meta"><time datetime="2020-04-16">2 days ago</time></div></div></div><div class="article-entry d-flex d-md-block"><div class="article-img"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/2020/04/16/live-the-erick-erickson-show-supply-chains/"><img width="1400" height="875" src="https://theresurgent.com/wp-content/uploads/erick-21-copy-1400x875.jpeg" class="auto-size" alt="" /></a><div class="author-meta offset-meta"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/erick-erickson/" class="avatar"><img src="https://theresurgent.com/wp-content/uploads/erick-20-100x100.jpg" alt="Erick Erickson" class="avatar"></a> <span>by <a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/erick-erickson/">Erick Erickson</a></span></div></div><div class="article-content"><h2><a href="https://theresurgent.com/2020/04/16/live-the-erick-erickson-show-supply-chains/">LIVE: The Erick Erickson Show &#8211; Supply Chains</a></h2><div class="article-excerpt"><p>You should really subscribe to my Substack channel. The Erick Erickson Show is live! Here&#8217;s the plan for today: Hour 1 Georgia audit by county Sonny Perdue WGXA in Macon Experts and curation Mic &hellip;</p></div><div class="author-meta post-meta"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/erick-erickson/" class="avatar"><img src="https://theresurgent.com/wp-content/uploads/erick-20-100x100.jpg" alt="Erick Erickson" class="avatar"></a> <span>by <a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/erick-erickson/">Erick Erickson</a></span></div><div class="post-meta time-meta"